(backbones) 

1. N-COUNT Your backbone is the column of small linked bones down the middle of your back. 脊骨 

2. N-UNCOUNT If you say that someone has no backbone , you think that they do not have the courage to do things which need to be done. 骨气 [oft with brd-neg] 

